headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Nucor Stock Falls as US, Mexico Negotiate on Steel Tariffs
summary: The S&P 500 slipped 0.3% on Wednesday, June 11, as investors weighed softer-than-expected inflation data and progress on U.S.-China trade talks.
